  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为MTDome的GUI工具设计一个类结构。核心是一个Model类，它要管理一个Reporter来发射各种信号。另外还需要一个TabTemplate作为所有标签页的基类。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Model",
        "Reporter",
        "TabTemplate"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，Model和Reporter是组合关系。Reporter会发射哪些具体信号？我需要确定这些信号类的名称。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Model",
        "Reporter"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Reporter需要发射四类信号：遥测数据SignalTelemetry、故障码SignalFaultCode、运动状态SignalMotion，还有设备状态SignalState。这些信号都放在mtdomegui命名空间里。TabTemplate则放在guitool命名空间，作为通用工具类。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SignalTelemetry",
        "SignalFaultCode",
        "SignalMotion",
        "SignalState",
        "TabTemplate",
        "guitool",
        "mtdomegui"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经添加了命名空间结构。现在处理继承关系：TabApertureShutter和TabFigure都继承自TabTemplate。TabApertureShutter组合Model，并且一个TabApertureShutter包含六个TabFigure。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TabApertureShutter",
        "TabFigure",
        "TabTemplate",
        "Model"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，比例关系是1对6。还有，TabFigure也要组合Model，这样每个图形标签页都能访问模型数据。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TabFigure",
        "Model"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "关于信号连接，我考虑让TabApertureShutter直接connect到那四个信号类。这样设计可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TabApertureShutter",
        "SignalTelemetry",
        "SignalFaultCode",
        "SignalMotion",
        "SignalState"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，Reporter到信号的关系应该是emit而不是connect。Reporter负责发射信号，TabApertureShutter负责连接接收。这两个关系类型不能搞混。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Reporter",
        "SignalTelemetry",
        "SignalFaultCode",
        "SignalMotion",
        "SignalState"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "已修正。现在结构清晰了：Reporter用emit()发射四个信号，TabApertureShutter用connect()接收这四个信号，同时它组合Model并包含六个TabFigure，每个TabFigure也组合Model。",
